name: Pinball FX2 VR
summary: Experience digital pinball as never before in Pinball FX2 VR, a groundbreaking new pinball game from the digital pinball pioneers at Zen Studios! Pinball FX2 VR features advanced physics, detailed 3D graphics, original table designs, and a robust set of social features and scoreboards making for an engaging VR experience you won’t find elsewhere.
